<p>Updates to the Steam Client have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Steam Client</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Fixed in-game overlay causing a crash for users running Windows XP without Service Pack 2 installed<br/><li>Fixed mouse clicks in-game sometimes not registering in the correct position for the in-game overlay<br/><li>Reduced CPU usage when using chat and group chat<br/><li>Reduced CPU usage while idle on the Store and Community tabs<br/><li>Fixed Steam windows showing up in the task-bar but impossible to restore</li></li></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
