(0, '2007-11-06', 'Steam Now Accepts Clickandbuy Payment Solution', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1293\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Starting today, you can purchase games on Steam using the ClickandBuy e-payment method. ClickandBuy\'s wide range of supported payment methodsincluding direct debit, ELV, online bank transfers, telephone billing, and credit cardsmakes it easier than ever to purchase and download a broad selection of game titles from dozens of leading publishers and independent developers. <br/><br/>For a limited time, ClickandBuy is offering Steam customers a $5 (USD) credit toward a future purchase with your first transaction using ClickandBuy. Simply select ClickandBuy as your payment method at checkout to save. <br/><br/>The new payment method is available to Steam customers across North America and the majority of European countries.</p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(0, '2007-11-13', NULL, '<div class=\"details\" id=\"November 13, 2007\" style=\"display: block;\">
