(0, '2011-06-01', 'Steam client update released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_5597\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>A Steam client update is now available. To apply the update, click the File menu inside of Steam and then select \"Check for Steam Client Updates...\".  The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Steam</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Fixes Steam not waiting for an in-progress Cloud sync to complete before launching a game.<br/><li>Fixed parental control check for Games For Windows games<br/><li>Fixed an issue where a user with no friend and no invite sent would not be able to view and accept a pending invite.<br/><li>Fix game file validation when opted into a game beta<br/><li>Improved Steam Guard feedback for expired email codes<br/><li>Improved overlay compatibility with Direct3D 11 games using the latest D3D SDK version<br/></li></li></li></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
