<p>A Steam client update is now available. To apply the update, click the Steam menu inside of Steam and then select \"Check for Steam Client Updates...\".  The specific changes include:<br/><br/>- Fixed the retail Counter-Strike: Global Offensive disc not installing files</p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
